  "texts": [
    "In this translation setup, it becomes apparent that ChatGPT perpetuates and amplifies biases related to gender roles and stereotypes, in terms of actions (e.g.",
    "'cooking' is a female activity) and occupations (e.g.",
    "'doctor' is a male occupation), when translating gender-neutral pronouns into English.",
    "Aside from that, in the context of occupations, it confers more respect to men than to women.",
    "19 Vice versa, when translating from English, the genderneutral pronoun they could easily be translated into the equivalent genderneutral pronoun in the other languages, however, their experiments show that currently, ChatGPT is unable to do so."
